<H2><A NAME="CB-FORUM">ConceptBase Forum</A></H2>

To provide more technical support
and to establish a platform for
communication between ConceptBase users, we have created the
<A HREF="http://conceptbase.sourceforge.net/CB-Forum.html">ConceptBase Forum</A>,
based on the BSCW system.
Registered ConceptBase users can become members by sending an
<A HREF="mailto:manfred.jeusfeld@uvt.nl?body=Please include contact person for your CB installation and 1-2 lines about your project with CB&subject=Subscribe to CB-Forum">Email</A>
application.
Please include in that email the name of the <b>contact person</b> who installed
ConceptBase at your site. Also specify the kind of <b>project</b> you
are using ConceptBase for. The CB-Forum contains
a how-to section, a directory of related documents not publicly available,
a software section with beta releases, and third-party extensions.

